----------------------------------------------------------------- ___________ - - How to use this -___________- Resize this window : when you press the PageDown key, you should see the next picture, centered. If not, go back, resize the window and try again. Once you have found the right size, hold the PageDown key pressed. ----------------------------------------------------------------- More about the topic : http://www.loria.fr/~lepetit/mangaribouPlayer.html (archive) http://www.multimania.com/vyger/humour.html (archive) http://www.aps.ch/~claudio/Perl/cine (Perl viewer) (C) 1999 by Bertrand Bram dit Saint-Amand (bertrand.bram@usa.net) English translation : E.
